Agent Ryann,

	Welcome to your moral crusade for the next few months.
Your task is to hunt down an ex-KGB covert operative codenamed
"BOREAS". Learn their secrets, analyze their tactics, find their
goals and motives, and hunt him before he can unleash devastation
among the United States and its allies. Who knows what is at play,
but we know his motive is to revive the Soviet Union out of its 
dying breath. Make sure this does not happen, nobody knows how many
lives are at stake.

Good Luck Ryann.

